00:36:12.500 --> 00:36:15.416
- He will not come out alive.
- Yes.

538
00:36:15.500 --> 00:36:17.125
When you hear of a death.

539
00:36:17.208 --> 00:36:20.458
- it's about him.
- He's going to die there.

540
00:36:20.541 --> 00:36:22.041
- There is no...
- Wait a minute.

541
00:36:22.125 --> 00:36:26.750
Are you saying that he will die before
the rituals are completed?

542
00:36:26.833 --> 00:36:27.791
- Yes!
- Yes!

543
00:36:27.875 --> 00:36:31.000
Don't worry about it!
Calm your mind.

544
00:36:31.083 --> 00:36:32.125
You'll see what happens.

545
00:36:32.208 --> 00:36:34.666
Chiefs. let us bow to the King.

546
00:36:34.750 --> 00:36:37.125
Your Highness.

547
00:38:33.250 --> 00:38:35.916
WHEN SHOOTING A FILM
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED.

548
00:38:36.000 --> 00:38:40.625
